---
import ProfileImage from "../../assets/ProfileImage.astro";
import Badge from "../../assets/Badge.astro";
---

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:gap-6 md:gap-8 items-center">
  <div class="md:order-1">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:gap-2 mb-3 sm:mb-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-3 md:gap-4">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-2 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105">
          <ProfileImage />
        </div>
        <Badge class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium">Disponible para trabajar</Badge>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h1 class="font-title text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-8 tracking-tighter transition-colors">
      <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Hola soy</span>
      <span class="text-yellow-500 dark:text-yellow-400"> Daniel</span>
      <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">, </span>
      <span class="relative group inline-block">
        <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Desarrollador Web.</span>
          <span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -bottom-1 left-0 h-1.5 w-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-500 transition-all duration-500 ease-out group-hover:w-full"></span>

    </h1>

    <p class="font-body text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 sm:mb-8 md:mb-10 max-w-3xl transition-colors">
  Me encanta <strong >imaginar</strong>, 
  <strong>crear</strong> y <strong>dar vida</strong> a 
  <span class="relative inline-block">
    <span class="underline decoration-indigo-400 decoration-2 underline-offset-4">proyectos web</span>
  </span> 
  que no solo funcionen, sino que <strong>inspiren</strong> a quienes los usan. 
  Mi objetivo es seguir creciendo como 
  <strong class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400">desarrollador</strong> 
  mientras aporto soluciones que hagan la experiencia digital m√°s 
  humana y <strong>efectiva</strong>.
</p>


    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 sm:gap-4 md:gap-6 mt-2 sm:mt-3 md:mt-4">
      <a
        href="#contacto"
        class="px-5 sm:px-6 md:px-8 py-3 sm:py-3.5 md:py-4 text-base sm:text-md md:text-lg bg-indigo-600 text-white font-medium rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-indigo-500 hover:text-white dark:bg-indigo-700 dark:hover:bg-indigo-600 dark:text-white dark:hover:text-white transition-all focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 dark:focus:ring-indigo-400 transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        Contacto
      </a>
      
      <a
        href="/curriculumProfesional-Daniel.pdf"
        download
        class="px-5 sm:px-6 md:px-8 py-3 sm:py-3.5 md:py-4 text-base sm:text-md md:text-lg bg-white text-indigo-600 font-medium rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-indigo-400 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-indigo-200 dark:focus:ring-indigo-900 transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        Descargar CV
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  
</div>